@startuml sequence_diagram_laporan
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Sequence Diagram Lihat Laporan\nSistem Prediksi Penyebaran DBD

actor "Pengguna" as User
participant "Halaman\nLaporan" as Page
participant "Controller\nLaporan" as Controller
database "Database" as DB

User -> Page : Buka menu Laporan
activate Page

Page -> Controller : Request data awal
activate Controller

Controller -> DB : SELECT tahun FROM kasus_bulanan
activate DB
DB --> Controller : Return daftar tahun
deactivate DB

Controller --> Page : Kirim data filter
Page --> User : Tampilkan halaman laporan\ndengan filter

== Filter dan Tampilkan Laporan ==

User -> Page : Pilih filter:\n- Tahun\n- Jenis Laporan

Page -> Controller : Request laporan\n{tahun, jenis}
activate Controller

alt Laporan Per Bulan
    Controller -> DB : SELECT * FROM kasus_bulanan\nWHERE tahun = ?
    activate DB
    DB --> Controller : Return data bulanan
    deactivate DB
    
else Laporan Per Wilayah
    Controller -> DB : SELECT wilayah, COUNT(*)\nFROM pasien_dbd\nGROUP BY wilayah
    activate DB
    DB --> Controller : Return data wilayah
    deactivate DB
end

Controller -> Controller : Hitung statistik:\n- Total, Rata-rata\n- Tertinggi, Terendah

Controller --> Page : Kirim data laporan

Page -> Page : Render grafik (Chart.js)
Page -> Page : Render tabel data

Page --> User : Tampilkan:\n- Grafik trend\n- Tabel detail\n- Statistik ringkasan

deactivate Controller

== Export Laporan ==

User -> Page : Klik Export PDF/Excel
Page -> Controller : Request export
activate Controller
Controller -> Controller : Generate file
Controller --> Page : File download
Page --> User : Download file
deactivate Controller

deactivate Page

@enduml
